### 4.5 Design System (Doc 09 — Build Directly From This)

- **3 Design Pillars:** Fresh & Vibrant · Rounded & Soft · Real Photography (dummy images in development)
- **Primary Green:** `#2D6A4F` | **Accent Orange:** `#FF6B35` | **Background:** `#FAFAF8`
- **Font:** Inter (system fallback: SF Pro on iOS, Roboto on Android)
- **Spacing grid:** 4px base unit
- **Minimum touch target:** 48dp for all interactive elements
- **Gesture activation time:** Long-press 300ms (forgiving, intentional)
- **Animations:** 60fps, never abrupt. Lock = satisfying click. Never = dish slides away. Acceptance = gentle checkmark.
- Combo card UI: combo name + component thumbnails on card. Meal Detail page is tabbed.
- Snacks slot: schema supports it (`planner.snacks_ref`), UI deferred to Phase 1 (confirmed)
- Notification permission: prompted at Onboarding Step 7 (confirmed)
- 'Recipe coming soon' placeholder: needed for 450+ dishes without Level 3 at launch — Claude will design this component

